---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="What is ManyTool | ManyTool" description="ManyTool 플랫폼 소개 및 사용 목적 안내 페이지입니다.">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black">What is ManyTool</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">ManyTool은 다양한 온라인 테스트와 도구를 제공하는 웹 기반 툴 플랫폼입니다.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">ManyTool is a web platform that provides various online tools, tests, games, and maps that users can access directly in their browser.</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-700"><a class="underline" href="/ai-search">AI 검색 최적화 운영 원칙 보기</a></p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
